						<h3><span id="How_do_I_create_maps?"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="How_do_I_create_maps.3F">How do I create maps?</span></h3>
						<p>
							This is a general RMXP question, not one specifically about Essentials. There are plenty of guides on how to use RMXP on the Internet.
						</p><p>
							There are some aspects of mapping (e.g.&nbsp;terrain tags) that are specific to Essentials, though. These aspects are documented on this wiki.
						</p>
