						<h3><span id="Where_can_I_find_resources?"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Where_can_I_find_resources.3F">Where can I find resources?</span></h3>
						<p>
							The wiki is not a place to upload and store resources such as sprites, tilesets and music. These things can easily be found on the Internet, though.
						</p><p>
							If you want custom scripts, such as one for a new&nbsp;mini-game, find the appropriate article and see what's in it. There may also be related tutorials, which often have scripts in them. Remember to credit the tutorial's author!
						</p>
